# Memory Management and Performance Optimization

**Activation Mode:** Model Decision
**Description:** Apply when working on performance optimization, memory usage, resource management, or performance-critical code

## Image Optimization
- Optimize images for mobile: use appropriate formats and sizes
- Implement lazy loading for images
- Use React Native Fast Image for better performance
- Cache images appropriately to reduce network requests

## List Performance
- Use FlatList or SectionList for large lists instead of ScrollView
- Implement proper keyExtractor and getItemLayout for better performance
- Use removeClippedSubviews for very long lists
- Implement lazy loading for list items when appropriate

## Memory Management
- Implement proper cleanup in useEffect hooks
- Avoid memory leaks in event listeners and subscriptions
- Use WeakMap and WeakSet when appropriate
- Clean up timers and intervals properly
- Remove navigation listeners on component unmount

## Performance Optimization
- Use React.memo, useMemo, and useCallback to prevent unnecessary re-renders
- Optimize bundle size and reduce JavaScript thread blocking
- Use InteractionManager for heavy operations
- Implement proper state management to avoid prop drilling
- Use Hermes JavaScript engine for better performance

## React Native Specific Optimizations
- Minimize bridge communications between JavaScript and native code
- Use native driver for animations when possible
- Implement proper keyboard handling to avoid performance issues
- Optimize startup time and reduce time to interactive
- Use proper debugging tools (Flipper, React Native Debugger) for performance profiling